descriptions.luck: Luck of the entity for loot tables
descriptions.attack_damage: Attack damage dealt by the entity

descriptions.ADD_SCALAR: Multiplies the base value (additive with other scalars)

lore.description: Item lore lines with MiniMessage formatting

unstackable.description: Whether the item cannot be stacked

injectId.description: Whether to inject Oraxen item ID into NBT

color.description: RGB color for leather armor, potions, maps (e.g., '255, 128, 0' or '#FF8000')

template.description: Template item ID to inherit from

Enchantments.description: Map of enchantment key to level

AttributeModifiers.description: Attribute modifiers to apply to the item

PersistentData.description: Custom persistent data to store on the item

damage_block_break.description: Whether breaking blocks damages the item

damage_entity_hit.description: Whether hitting entities damages the item

max_stack_size.description: Maximum stack size for this item

can_always_eat.description: Whether item can be eaten when not hungry

slot.description: Equipment slot this item can be equipped to

swappable.description: Can be swapped with other equipment

damage_on_hurt.description: Takes damage when player is hurt

group.description: Cooldown group (items in same group share cooldown)

repair.description: Allows items to be repaired with custom materials (deprecated on 1.21+, use repaired_by component)

oraxen_item.description: Oraxen item ID to use as repair material

bleeding.description: Causes targets to bleed over time, dealing damage at intervals

duration.description: Total duration of bleeding effect in ticks

shaped_block.description: Allows creating custom stairs, slabs, doors, trapdoors, grates, and bulbs (transparent blocks) using waxed copper blocks as base

type.description: Type of shaped block: STAIR, SLAB, DOOR, TRAPDOOR, GRATE, BULB

custom_variation.description: Custom variation (1-4, maps to copper oxidation states)

lifeleech.description: Heals the player when dealing damage to entities

witherskull.description: Launches a wither skull projectile that applies wither effect

charged.description: Whether the skull is charged (blue, more powerful)

spear_lunge.description: Enables a charge-and-lunge attack with model swapping for spears

charge_ticks.description: Ticks to fully charge the lunge

max_range.description: Maximum range to hit targets during lunge

min_damage.description: Minimum damage dealt during lunge (at 0% charge)

knockback.description: Knockback applied to targets hit by the lunge

hitbox_radius.description: Hitbox radius for lunge hit detection (higher = easier to hit off-center)

max_targets.description: Maximum number of entities hit per lunge

min_charge_percent.description: Minimum charge percentage required to attack (0-1)

max_hold_ticks.description: Maximum time to hold charge (ticks) before cancelling

smooth_frames.description: Number of intermediate animation frames used during charge

intermediate_models.description: List of intermediate model paths for smooth charge animation

skin.description: Defines an item as a skin that can be applied to skinnable items

consume.description: Whether the skin is consumed when applied

consumable_potion_effects.description: Applies potion effects when the item is consumed

effects.description: List of potion effects to apply on consumption

aura.description: Creates a particle aura effect around the player when holding the item

skinnable.description: Marks an item as skinnable, allowing skins to be applied to it

bottledexp.description: Stores player experience into experience bottles

harvesting.description: Automatically harvests and replants crops when broken

soulbound.description: Keeps the item in inventory on death instead of dropping

music_disc.description: Custom music disc with custom sounds (deprecated on 1.21+, use jukeboxPlayable component)

song.description: Sound resource location for the music

noteblock.description: Creates custom blocks using noteblock states (up to 775 variations)

canIgnite.description: Whether the block can be ignited

furniture.description: Places items as interactive furniture entities in the world

item.description: Alternative Oraxen item ID to display

farmland_required.description: Whether farmland is required for placement

farmblock_required.description: Whether farmblock is required for placement

rotatable.description: Whether furniture can be rotated after placement

barriers.description: List of barrier block positions relative to furniture

hat.description: Allows items to be worn as hats (deprecated on 1.21.2+, use equippable component instead)

commands.description: Executes commands when the item is used

permission.description: Permission required to use the item

one_usage.description: Whether the item is consumed on use

fireball.description: Launches a fireball projectile that explodes on impact

misc.description: Miscellaneous item properties like fire/lava damage resistance

burns_in_fire.description: Whether item burns in fire (deprecated, use damage_resistant)

burns_in_lava.description: Whether item burns in lava (deprecated, use damage_resistant)

breaks_from_cactus.description: Whether item breaks from cactus (deprecated, use damage_resistant)

break_music_discs.description: Whether item can break music discs

smelting.description: Automatically smelts mined blocks into their smelted form

chorusblock.description: Creates custom blocks using chorus plant states (up to 63 variations)

is_falling.description: Whether the block falls like sand

immovable.description: Whether the block can be moved by pistons

thor.description: Summons lightning bolts on the target location when attacking

lightning_bolts_amount.description: Number of lightning bolts to summon

efficiency.description: Modifies mining speed for tools beyond vanilla efficiency

custom.description: Custom mechanic with configurable actions and conditions

durability.description: Custom durability behavior for items (deprecated on 1.20.5+, use durability component instead)

food.description: Legacy food behavior (deprecated on 1.20.5+, use food component instead)

effects.description: Potion effects to apply on consume

armor_effects.description: Applies potion effects while wearing armor pieces

effects.description: List of potion effects to apply

energyblast.description: Fires an energy blast projectile that damages entities in its path

itemtype.description: Defines custom item type behavior for categorization

watering.description: Waters farmland blocks to hydrate them

consumable.description: Legacy consumable behavior for items (deprecated on 1.21.2+, use consumable component)

backpack.description: Provides portable storage that persists with the item

backpack_cosmetic.description: Displays a cosmetic backpack on the player's back using packet-based armor stands

slot.description: Equipment slot that triggers backpack display

model.description: Model to display as the backpack

visible_to_self.description: Whether the backpack is visible to the player themselves

knockback_strike.description: Knocks back enemies after a certain number of consecutive hits with particle effects

required_hits.description: Number of consecutive hits required to trigger knockback

play_sound.description: Play sound effect on knockback trigger

reset_time.description: Time in ticks before hit counter resets (20 ticks = 1 second)

show_counter.description: Show hit counter (method exists but actionbar is removed)

bigmining.description: Mines blocks in an area around the targeted block

stringblock.description: Creates custom blocks using tripwire states (up to 127 variations)

generate_model.description: Whether to auto-generate model from textures

parent_model.description: Parent model to inherit display properties from

oneOf.description: List of texture paths for layered 2D items
Named texture map for block models (top, side, bottom, etc.)

model.description: Path to existing JSON model file (without .json)

models.description: Additional models map. Keys are aliases, values are model paths. Auto-registered as oraxen:<itemId>/<key>. Example: { opened: default/turntable_opened }

custom_model_data.description: Specific CustomModelData value (auto-generated if not set)

pulling_models.description: Models for bow pulling animation stages

pulling_textures.description: Textures for bow pulling animation stages

hand_animation_on_swap.description: Play hand animation on item swap

generated_model_path.description: Custom path for generated model output
